CHANGELOG

0.3 - 2014-04-13
- added default mirrors for Fedora and Scientific Linux
- folder structures are now created in lower-case and stripped depending on mirror and distro
- file system path is displayed after downloading (just c&p into cobbler or Spacewalk/Satellite/SUSE Manager WebUI)

0.2 - 2014-04-11
- updated support for other EL-like distros (Fedora, Scientific Linux)

0.1 - 2014-04-10
- initial release
